{"word":"G5238 - ὑπερέκεινα - hyperékeina - hoop-er-ek'-i-nah - Beyond","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερέκεινα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperékeina</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-ek'-i-nah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beyond</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அப்புறமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"beyond"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and the neuter plural of <a href=\"#/G1565 - ἐκεῖνος - ekeînos - ek-i'-nos/1565\">G1565</a>; <i>above those</i> parts, that is, <i>still farther:</i> - beyond.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}